UDB [UDB=(2,2)] contents:
LAB@[UDB=(2,2)][LB=0] #macrocells=4, #inputs=8, #pterms=6
{
    [McSlotId=0]:     MacroCell: Name=\ADC:soc_out\, Mode=(D-Register) @ [UDB=(2,2)][LB=0][MC=0]
        Total # of inputs        : 6
        Total # of product terms : 2
        List of special equations: 
            Clock  = (Net_10) => Global
            Clock Enable: PosEdge(\ADC:bSAR_SEQ:enable\)
        Main Equation            : 2 pterms
        (
              !\ADC:soc_out\ * \ADC:Net_3830\ * !\ADC:bSAR_SEQ:load_period\ * 
              \ADC:bSAR_SEQ:state_1\ * !\ADC:bSAR_SEQ:cnt_tc\
            + !\ADC:soc_out\ * !\ADC:bSAR_SEQ:load_period\ * 
              \ADC:bSAR_SEQ:soc_in\ * !\ADC:bSAR_SEQ:state_1\
        );
        Output = \ADC:soc_out\ (fanout=3)
        Properties               : 
        {
        }

    [McSlotId=1]:     MacroCell: Name=\ADC:bSAR_SEQ:state_1\, Mode=(D-Register) @ [UDB=(2,2)][LB=0][MC=1]
        Total # of inputs        : 4
        Total # of product terms : 2
        List of special equations: 
            Clock  = (Net_10) => Global
            Clock Enable: PosEdge(\ADC:bSAR_SEQ:enable\)
        Main Equation            : 2 pterms
        (
              !\ADC:soc_out\ * !\ADC:Net_3830\ * !\ADC:bSAR_SEQ:load_period\ * 
              \ADC:bSAR_SEQ:state_1\
            + \ADC:soc_out\ * !\ADC:bSAR_SEQ:load_period\ * 
              !\ADC:bSAR_SEQ:state_1\
        );
        Output = \ADC:bSAR_SEQ:state_1\ (fanout=2)
